Senior Citizens of Davis (SCD) is the principal, NonProfit Organizations nonprofit support organization supporting the Davis Senior Center. They provide funding for the Davis Senior Center to publish its monthly newsletter, The Senior Scene.
A copy of the 2008 Bylaws (current as of this posting in September 2012), is available here in PDF form. File(SCDbylaws20082012+.pdf)
Currently, membership in SCD includes a mailed subscription to The Senior Scene.  Or you can get a PDF of the latest issue from the City of Davis website about the Davis Senior Center.
